Decide you want pizza!
Think of your fav pizza joint.
Look at their online menu.
Order online-choose your favorite pizza and extras.
Pay through the website and enter your delivery address.
Await your pizza delivery.

If you want to make changes to your order after you submit it, you will have to call the company.
If you want to determine the time your pizza will be ready for pickup, please look at the app under "orders".